lead_paragraph: Virginia Tech entered Atlantic Coast Conference play with a sparkling record and several quality wins to its credit, but the Hokies hadn't faced a ranked foe all season.

headline.print_headline: Bibbs Lifts Hokies to 89-75 Upset of No. 5 Duke
